al\nor noisy experimental condition and recovers the time information from waveform\nsamples successfully and precisely.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Apr 2023 09:16:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Apr 2023 11:16:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-01"}
