I/MIDI. With\nmid-IR interferometric data, we directly confirm the transition disc nature of\nsix circumbinary discs around post-AGB binary systems. Future observational and\nmodelling efforts are needed to progress in our understanding of the structure,\norigin, and evolution of these transition discs\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Apr 2023 12:04:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 May 2023 07:41:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-04"}
