 input step-strain\nprofile. Meanwhile, the NEVP model is further validated by comparison to a\nsteady Herschel--Bulkley fit of the material's flow curve.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Apr 2023 14:03:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-25"}
