d by an RMF, with the\nresolution set by the relative magnitude of the gating field and the RMF. The\nconcepts developed here lay a foundation for future closed-loop control schemes\nfor magnetic microrobots based on simultaneous inductive sensing and actuation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Apr 2023 14:45:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-25"}
